name: Welcome!
body:
### Bio

I am a software engineer living in San Francisco.

I am currently working at Xtime as an Integration Engineer.

My wife is the lovely and talented [Nancy Jeng](http://www.nancyjeng.com/)

[A Hailstone Sequence Calculator/Visualization using Meteor and D3.js](http://hailstone.meteor.com/)


[A simple Blackjack game using Spring MVC](http://brettsblackjack.heroku.com/)
